(February 16, 1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-8 : Present — Bergan, P. J., Coon, Gibson, Herlihy and Taylor, JJ.

(A) In the Matter of the Claim of Emily Vargas, Appellant, v. Julius Fine et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent. (B) George B. Ciccone et al., Respondents, v. Paul Bouthillette et al., Appellants.

[In each action] Motions to dismiss appeals granted by default, without costs.
